title: august 30: welcome to the late show with david letterman!
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the debut episodes of The Late Show with David Letterman on CBS. After, Maia revisits 2020’s pandemic-conscious VMAs. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
